"係咁掛住不如攞去做標本擺返係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"依d時候仲講得出依d野以為自己好好笑果種人<br />\n我屌你老母"},{"pid":"01ce275290cd5773a896f402306407472402ea7c","tid":744252,"uid":80294,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"20df42bd247aad41afbc47693dde36940a8dd62e","tid":744252,"uid":91502,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"0c00c4c7e1a43811953c34292ec9cc408f6f96c6","tid":744252,"uid":80294,"like":0,"dislike":11,"score":-11,"quote":{"pid":"377f70f27e5bf55cd94f9e209c2fa6a08b9d6b40","tid":744252,"uid":183588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-15T22:35:49.000Z","msg":"佢得八歲，我救佢唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我唔明點解佢要死，點解死嗰個唔係我，明明佢好好，冇做錯任何嘢，係我唔好，成日好忙冇乜時間陪佢，到想陪嘅時候已經陪唔到。<br />\n<br />\n我唔知我仲有啲乜嘢可以失去，佢死咗之後我發現所有我想要嘅嘢都唔及佢咁重要，我寧願放棄所有嘢換返佢返嚟。<br />\n<br />\n我喊咗幾日，晚晚訓唔到，其他人叫我唔好喊，life must go on，但我go on唔到。我不斷問屋企人攞佢嘅相，又係新舊電話反覆咁搵，俾我搵到百幾張相。八年影得百幾張相，我去個旅行一日都唔止啦，我對佢真係虧欠太多。<br />\n<br />\n我成日覺得佢仲係度，我唔想屋企人掉佢啲嘢，我驚佢返嚟唔見曬啲嘢會驚，會以為我哋唔要佢。有冇人知佢死咗之後會去邊？我第日有冇機會見返佢？<br />\n<br />\n仲有如果你哋有養寵物，記得要抽多啲時間陪佢，唔好等你有時間先陪，因為當你有時間嘅時候，佢可能已經冇時間。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/063302_b82623eba9925bb0bdce541893807605.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F063302_b82623eba9925bb0bdce541893807605.png&h=537ac9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T04:48:53.000Z","msg":"係咁掛住不如攞去做標本擺返係屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:17:54.000Z","msg":"依d時候仲講得出依d野以為自己好好笑果種人<br />\n我屌你老母"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:42:26.000Z","msg":"大把鬼佬攞隻狗條屍去做標本<br />\n擺係屋企做腳踏又有 做燈座又有<br />\n成個行業做到成行成市 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家我知香港都有幾檔<br />\n可能你未聽過啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4d5462c915d92fbfa38335dd6aae231c7e58603","tid":744252,"uid":129374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"因咩事死㗎? 八歲唔算好老呀."},{"pid":"e280bcc791709a3ab30dab20e7f1e655ba008877","tid":744252,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"我都有養史立莎家下4歲, 本來最親我, 但最近唔知發生咩事變左親我細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a44ad0f9a07518814b50a506e67698e1cb61824","tid":744252,"uid":183588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4d5462c915d92fbfa38335dd6aae231c7e58603","tid":744252,"uid":129374,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:47:16.000Z","msg":"因咩事死㗎? 八歲唔算好老呀."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:19:01.000Z","msg":"病死，帶去睇醫生但最後都係死咗。八歲唔係好老，我覺得佢仲可以陪多我八年。"},{"pid":"1cc12f91ffd2ffb7fb1b084f81bdf0a70835ff02","tid":744252,"uid":183588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e280bcc791709a3ab30dab20e7f1e655ba008877","tid":744252,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"我都有養史立莎家下4歲, 本來最親我, 但最近唔知發生咩事變左親我細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:19:20.000Z","msg":"好好珍惜"},{"pid":"b50ef932efda3d5fe3cee0606796e14903d83f47","tid":744252,"uid":53399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e280bcc791709a3ab30dab20e7f1e655ba008877","tid":744252,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T06:51:26.000Z","msg":"我都有養史立莎家下4歲, 本來最親我, 但最近唔知發生咩事變左親我細佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T07:20:27.000Z","msg":"你係咪呃過佢黎"},{"pid":"b7c6e4d823ab818eddd49c6f841a98fffc44903d","tid":744252,"uid":53399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20df42bd247aad41afbc47693dde36940a8dd62e","tid":744252,"uid":91502,"like":7,"dislike":2,"score":5,"quote":{"pi